{"tid":713942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「陶瓷刀係假利　我嘅刀係真鋒」","createTime":"2018-06-23T08:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T15:33:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5113c8ed4414a1e47bf6b361c00892c8585e21","tid":713942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180623/20429153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20429153&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=95912501\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20429153&h=b71e7270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180623/20429153</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月23日 <br />\n<br />\n「陶瓷刀係假利　我嘅刀係真鋒」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180623/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180623%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=14c258e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陶瓷刀以不易令食物氧化作賣點，惟市面上產品質素參差。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華叔73年來只鍾情鋼刀，無奈歲月洪流不停沖刷，近年陶瓷刀大行其道，鋒利度是鋼刀的十倍以上，而且硬度更僅次於鑽石，更有陶瓷刀製造商聲稱陶瓷刀可抗氧化、切洋葱不流淚、蘋果切後不會變黑等效果，加上外形美觀新潮，不少現代家庭都以陶瓷刀取代鋼刀。不過華叔卻嚏之以鼻，原來他的店舖於30年前亦曾經售賣陶瓷刀，但如今已絕迹店內，「最多用半年」。陶瓷刀雖亦可磨利，但華叔稱︰「磨完切多幾次都係唔利，嘥氣！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華叔一刀切開一吋布<br />\n<br />\n經華叔打磨的鋼刀，除可剃鬚，亦可切布、膠袋，華叔如老師講課般示範，將彈性布層層叠，摺成一吋多，只見刀子輕輕一𠝹，布塊便齊口被切開，見記者看得津津有味，華叔再拿起一透明包裝膠袋，直、橫、斜各三刀，「陶瓷刀係假利，我嘅刀係真鋒」。此刻的華叔，活像一位武林中人。<br />\n<br />\n華叔解釋，假利並不持久，陶瓷刀於高處墮下更會崩口，而經他打磨的鋼刀則是真鋒，是持久的，因此若客人想要買磨刀石親自磨刀，華叔會提醒只需一年磨一次。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘婉玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港故事：自創九石磨刀法　利刃剃手毛　一代刀師 嚇窒老外<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\nGOALCHASER掃黃　拉13個內地女<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港故事：自創九石磨刀法　利刃剃手毛　一代刀師 嚇窒老外"},{"pid":"fa1033a1c84ec1fbaa7ab7227b336a895b409e6d","tid":713942,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"匠+5"},{"pid":"adb0e071d6156168465d3d3823464ed2bf961983","tid":713942,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"蘋果生鏽唔係因為接觸到金屬刀具"},{"pid":"ecabc48abd7bbd06ff5a22503f3490be14ff52ec","tid":713942,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"陶瓷刀唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f6705ee84825b9490c3c7f9e206982a013bbcd","tid":713942,"uid":55568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"今時今日，梗係用紙皮整刀<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jvo86AHovFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fjvo86AHovFc&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a485705c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jvo86AHovFc</a>"},{"pid":"9b03e79d480a8439dcd63a53993f3e754d5cfa4f","tid":713942,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37f6705ee84825b9490c3c7f9e206982a013bbcd","tid":713942,"uid":55568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"今時今日，梗係用紙皮整刀<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jvo86AHovFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fjvo86AHovFc&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a485705c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jvo86AHovFc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"帶上飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a71e91f594e7b2242ca819821c8516e07cb7d79","tid":713942,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b03e79d480a8439dcd63a53993f3e754d5cfa4f","tid":713942,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37f6705ee84825b9490c3c7f9e206982a013bbcd","tid":713942,"uid":55568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"